26-jun-2001 v. 0.1.2

-Bugfix: error in stri[n]cmp on linux
-Added -t option for test runs showing response on stdout
-Added -l option for time limit on test
-Added -h option for specifying request headers
-Added -o option for csv output mode
-Cleaned up parameter parsing
-Graceful handling of DNS lookup failure
-Added first version of verifier code
-Added -b option to only output the body in test mode

27-mar-2001 v. 0.1.1

-Added handling of non-chunked responses with no Content-Length header
-Added handling of port numbers in urls
-Added response times to output
-Added error percentage to output

